verbose_text: All DFT calculations were carried out using the Vienna Ab initio Simulation Package (VASP).22 The PBE exchange correlation functional23 with the D3 dispersion-correction and Becke-Johnson damping24 together with the projector augmented wave (PAW) method25 was applied.
